o- BUILD AND RUN

    cargo build --release && cargo run -- --help

    It may be faster to call directly: ./target/release/crp --help

o- EXAMPLE

    This example will convert the color of the clothes on the brown bear (named Boob) 
    in input.jpg in the warehouse to green and save it in target.jpg, final output execution time

    ./target/release/crp --input-image input.jpg      \
                         --target-image target.jpg    \
                         --origin-color "118 173 214" \
                         --target-color "19 214 156"   
    42ms